# Mech_arm.py

The controll class of the arm.


# PCA9685.py

The control class of IC PCA9685 via i2c bus 


# joystick.py

The class for read the joystick made of arduino board and analog device.
Read action is implemented via the UART "/dev/ttyUSB0"


# joystick_usb.py

The class for read the USB Joystick.
Read action is implemented via "/dev/input/js0"


# test-code

The dircetor contains the test code.

## main.py

the main loop which is operating the arm depending the command from joystick
